{"tid":1758621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又派錢比黑警 遭「起底」警員將獲資助換車牌","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T07:20:23.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7bff7f07002fe89227d6b61c625fe85ec1dc00","tid":1758621,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"消息指，警方決定資助被「起底」的警務人員更換車牌，今天起接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n警方人事部發出通知，指鑑於有不少警員被「起底」，包括車牌號碼在不同公眾平台被公開，對警務人員及車輛安全造成潛在風險。<br />\n<br />\n警隊管理層決定以警察福利基金，資助受影響人員更換新車牌及新造車牌的開支，包括560元行政費及最多300元買新車牌，今天起接受申請，申請資格必須是車牌被起底的現職警務人員，每人可獲一次資助。"},{"pid":"70da9d854fa45f8a8c2fa757e3c71d175b3bfa8b","tid":1758621,"uid":20870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"要唔要整埋容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcaaa5eb9f630a35ce328114f54e657e993d1ea","tid":1758621,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70da9d854fa45f8a8c2fa757e3c71d175b3bfa8b","tid":1758621,"uid":20870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"要唔要整埋容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65111221bd6abd4f7e0f7981d08c3b057eeb472f","tid":1758621,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"可獲一次咁多<br />\n咁我起夠你十次啦"},{"pid":"312c682433c9c5de7ad9841fe761e50957f1bf29","tid":1758621,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"分分鐘係自己報料放上網，免費轉車牌"},{"pid":"4700319923044e975cb494cac75d7df3745c1777","tid":1758621,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"資助換埋老婆仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}